section.div: It would mean the world to me if I had 5 sponsors.

div.p: Hi, I'm Baris Al aka MutanPlex.
I'm also very passionate about anything Android, Windows, Linux and Web related and love messing around with the internals of things!
By sponsoring me you support my work and help me pay for costs like domain, hosting and also life expenses and allow me to spend more time on my projects.

You can always message on Discord at @mutanplex if you have any questions. This is also how you claim your rewards. Please do not try sending me a friend request, I will not accept people I don't recognise. Instead, join the Plexcord Server and you can private message me from there.
If you get an error trying to message me, go to the Plexcord Server => Server Settings => Privacy Settings => Check Allow DMs from other members in this server

div.b: Your fortune: Good news will come to you by mail
